  <brief_title>Doxycycline and Ceftriaxone in Suspected Early Lyme Neuroborreliosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Doxycycline and Ceftriaxone in Patients With Suspected Early Lyme Neuroborreliosis and Normal CSF Cell Count.</official_title>
