  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will compare doxycycline and ceftriaxone in treatment of patients with
      suspected early Lyme neuroborreliosis and normal CSF cell count. The study hypothesis is that
      the efficacy and adverse effects of both antibiotics are comparable.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
